<p>The gameplay video shows off most of the mechanics in the game. Unfortunately the boss fight somehow broke since the last time I have touched this game so I unfortunately couldn&#8217;t show it off <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f641.png" alt="ðŸ™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> It&#8217;s 30ish minutes soooo yah. I have photos and stuff of the menus so that you can get a quick look at it.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
